Tasks for week 2:
1) Obtain genomes for an "outgroup". This is similar to what we did with Streptococcus, but now we take the genomes from the Streptococcaceae family
that belog to diferent genera. The genera in the Streptoccocaceae family are: 
Floricoccus
Lactococcus
Lactovum
Okadaella

2) Annotate genomes with Prokka

3) Indentify orthologous genes (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5674930/, https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3531125/, https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/30395283)
